Title: An Operational Measure of Riskiness
Abstract: We propose a measure of riskiness of &ldquo;gambles&rdquo; (risky assets) that is objective: it depends only on the gamble and not on the decision maker. The measure is based on identifying for every gamble the critical wealth level below which it becomes &ldquo;risky&rdquo; to accept the gamble.
